Description: The Unmapped Concepts module, part of the larger SQUBA ecosystem, evaluates
    the distribution of NULL or unmapped (as defined by the user) concepts at the row and patient
    levels. The module will also assess the median number of unmapped values per patient, allowing
    the user to determine if unmapped values are dispersed across the whole cohort.
